data.oai_dc:dc: FASTA file containing 210 resolved alleles from intron 3 of the lactate dehydrogenase B (LDHB) gene sampled from 105 Common (Green-winged) Teal (Anas crecca). Populations (OW, Old World, NW, New World, Attu, Aleutian Islands, Shemya, Aleutian Islands, Adak, Aleutian Islands, Ugamak, Aleutian Islands) are defined within the file.
